@cpt_acid thanks for the help, I`m using UPC already:) 

Unfortunately, it doesn`t adjust the unit statistics with the mod (for example, bigger unit sizes in mostly any mod), so it`s not a solution (it only provides text for added units).

It would be easy to just copy/paste entries in PFM (from a mod into napmod.pack, as all mods have entries adjusting DLC units statistics already), but Tanauser changed their names to custom_unitsXX, so it takes eternity to find out which unit is which.
